Aims

Condition

Loading data

Encoding task

Is there a reaction time and accuracy difference?

Note that for the first participant, the responses were not saved correctly and have to be inverted.

There is strong evidence that RT are faster in the living condition (BF10 = 9.8489599^{22}), however there is also evidence that accuracy does not differ between the condition (BF01 = 4.91).

Recognition task

Are there RT difference between RFN?

This comparison showed a main effect of recognition type (BF10 = 183).
